description:
The Female Dating Archetypes course is the go-to resource for everyday men looking to get the most out of their bachelorhood! We teach necessary and practical skills on how to identify and attract almost any type of woman.

We will be going over the hows and whys of why learn these skills is imperative single men and in long term relationships. We delve into the specifics on how to attract many types of woman and how to maintain your confidence and poise along the way.

Our course consists of 13 video lectures total and each lecture is between five to ten minutes in length. Along with the detailed lectures, we provide a timeless EBook which will accompany you as one of your essentials to attracting different types of women.

The course is perfect for men who are just out of a relationship or have been single for significant amount of time. Nonetheless, much of the subject matter is a good refresher course for older or more experienced men as well. We look forward to hearing from you!
title: Female Dating Archetypes and How to Attract Each One
